  "general_provisions": "This resolution directs the Public Employees' Benefit Insurance Program to establish the Weight Management and Obesity Pilot Program.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This resolution:<hr><ltbullet>recognizes the existing bariatric surgery pilot program within the Public Employees' Benefit Insurance Program (PEHP); and<hr><ltbullet>directs PEHP to establish a new Weight Management and Obesity Pilot Program that combines the bariatric surgery pilot program with an option for GLP-1 coverage.",
